poodah.conf
Class JobConfig

java.lang.Object
  poodah.conf.JobConfig
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class JobConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class is crucial in the running of the client's map-reduce application. It is imperative that all information pertaining to client's map/reduce classes are set in this file. The map-reduce framework will make heavy use of this configuration file.

Author:
rajagarw, keweiz
